text:
The Chicago-set docuseries “City So Real” from Oak Park filmmaker Steve James has found a broadcast home.

The 5-part series will premiere on NatGeo on Oct. 29 and will be available to stream on Hulu afterward. https://t.co/xawvRnlwA4

text: Kyle Rittenhouse is scheduled for a hearing Friday that will focus on whether he will be sent to Wisconsin to face charges alleging he fatally shot two people and wounded a third during protests in Kenosha last month. https://t.co/OC5YH097zJ
